racecardEvent.overview: An 800m scamper, numbers 2,3,7,9,11,12 each have speed. THE BILLIONAIRE resumes, has won this track/trip and in good time from a wide draw. SHEEZASINGA and TROPICS resume, both placed decent 3rds this track/trip first-up last time in. EYEWITNESS draws the best for Ryan Maloney, looks a lay at the morning odds. ONE PENNY is new blood, resuming for Chris Anderson. Won her trial stylishly, betting will be a great guide.   Hard to look beyond IDONEUS which relished the drop back to this distance last start and after the claim for Angela Jones carries a mere 52.5 kg's.
